description: This file contains implementation of utility functions related to DataModelAgent in a C-based project, including plugin info management, source info parsing, object registration, API resolution checks, object info parsing, and function interface parsing for TR-069-like data models.

methods.name: ANSC_HANDLE DslhDmagntCreatePluginInfo(ANSC_HANDLE hThisObject)
methods.description: Creates and initializes a new PluginInfo structure, returning a handle to it.

methods.name: ANSC_STATUS DslhDmagntRemovePluginInfo(ANSC_HANDLE hThisObject,ANSC_HANDLE hPluginInfo)
methods.description: Removes and frees resources associated with a PluginInfo structure.

methods.name: ANSC_STATUS DslhDmagntParseSourceInfo(ANSC_HANDLE hThisObject,ANSC_HANDLE hXMLNode,ANSC_HANDLE hPluginInfo)
methods.description: Parses source/library information from an XML node and loads associated library, APIs, and metadata.

methods.name: ANSC_STATUS DslhDmagntParseSourceName(ANSC_HANDLE hThisObject,ANSC_HANDLE hXMLNode,char * pName)
methods.description: Retrieves the library filename (with .so extension) from an XML node.

methods.name: ANSC_STATUS DslhDmagntRegisterDataModelObject(ANSC_HANDLE hThisObject,ANSC_HANDLE hObjectNode,char * pParentObjName,ANSC_HANDLE hPluginInfo,BOOL bPopulateTree)
methods.description: Registers a data model object described in an XML node into the controller, including handling tables and nested objects.

methods.name: BOOL DslhDmagntCheckApiResolved(ANSC_HANDLE hThisObject,ANSC_HANDLE hXMLNode,ANSC_HANDLE hPluginInfo)
methods.description: Checks whether all APIs used in specified XML nodes are resolved (i.e., their function pointers are valid).

methods.name: BOOL lookforUnresolvedApiInParamList(ANSC_HANDLE hXMLNode,ANSC_HANDLE hPluginInfo)
methods.description: Helper function to check for unresolved APIs in parameter lists within an XML node.

methods.name: BOOL lookforUnresolvedApiInObject(ANSC_HANDLE hXMLNode,ANSC_HANDLE hPluginInfo)
methods.description: Helper function to recursively check all functions and child objects within an XML node for unresolved APIs.

methods.name: BOOL DslhDmagntCheckBaseObjNames(ANSC_HANDLE hThisObject,char * pRootName,ANSC_HANDLE hXMLNode)
methods.description: Checks whether all base objects referenced in XML are registered or can be created, creating missing ones if necessary.

methods.name: ANSC_HANDLE DslhDmagntParseObjFuncInfo(ANSC_HANDLE hThisObject,ANSC_HANDLE hXMLNode,ANSC_HANDLE hPluginInfo)
methods.description: Parses function definitions within an XML node to link API functions to the interface structure.

methods.name: ANSC_HANDLE DslhDmagntParseRootFuncInfo(ANSC_HANDLE hThisObject,ANSC_HANDLE hXMLNode,ANSC_HANDLE hAtomFunc)
methods.description: Parses root-level function definitions for TR-069 interfaces from XML.

methods.name: ANSC_STATUS DslhDmagntParseObjectInfo(ANSC_HANDLE hThisObject,ANSC_HANDLE hObjectNode,char * pParentObjName,ANSC_HANDLE hPluginInfo,ANSC_HANDLE hObjectDesp)
methods.description: Parses object information from XML, including name, type, hierarchy, and API functions.

methods.name: DslhDmagntParseObjectInfo
methods.description: Parses object information from an XML node, including name, type, hierarchy, and API functions.

methods.name: DslhDmagntParseSourceInfo
methods.description: Parses source/library info from an XML node, loads associated library and metadata.

methods.name: DslhDmagntParseSourceName
methods.description: Retrieves the library filename with .so extension from an XML node.

methods.name: DslhDmagntRegisterDataModelObject
methods.description: Registers a data model object based on parsed XML info, including handling nested objects and tables.

methods.name: DslhDmagntParseObjFuncInfo
methods.description: Parses function definitions within an XML node and links API functions to the interface structure.

methods.name: lookforUnresolvedApiInParamList
methods.description: Helper to recursively check parameter list functions for unresolved APIs.

methods.name: lookforUnresolvedApiInObject
methods.description: Recursively checks objects and their API functions for unresolved APIs.

methods.name: DslhDmagntCheckBaseObjNames
methods.description: Verifies and creates missing base objects referenced in XML.

methods.name: ANSC_HANDLE DslhDmagntParseParamArray(ANSC_HANDLE hThisObject,ANSC_HANDLE hXMLNode,ANSC_HANDLE hPluginInfo)
methods.description: Parses an array of parameters from an XML node into internal data structures.

methods.name: ANSC_STATUS DslhDmagntParseParamInfo(ANSC_HANDLE hThisObject,ANSC_HANDLE hParamNode,ANSC_HANDLE hPluginInfo,ANSC_HANDLE hParamDesp)
methods.description: Retrieves and sets parameter information from an XML node into a parameter descriptor.

methods.name: ANSC_STATUS DslhDmagntUnloadDataModelObject(ANSC_HANDLE hThisObject,ANSC_HANDLE hObjectNode,char * pParentObjName)
methods.description: Unloads/de-registers a data model object based on its XML node and parent object name.

methods.name: BOOL GetParamUlongValue_X_CISCO_COM_COSADataModel(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext,char * ParamName,ULONG * pUlong)
methods.description: Retrieves ULONG parameters for the 'X_CISCO_COM_COSADataModel' object.

methods.name: BOOL GetParamUlongValue_COSADataModel(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext,char * ParamName,ULONG * pUlong)
methods.description: Retrieves ULONG parameters such as Version and counts for the COSA DataModel.

methods.name: ULONG GetEntryCount_COSADataModel(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext)
methods.description: Returns the count of registered data model plugin info entries.

methods.name: ANSC_HANDLE GetEntry_COSADataModel(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext,ULONG nIndex,PULONG pInsNumber)
methods.description: Retrieves a specific COSA DataModel entry by index.

methods.name: BOOL IsUpdated_COSADataModel(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext)
methods.description: Checks whether the COSA DataModel plugin info list has been updated.

methods.name: ULONG Synchronize_COSADataModel(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext)
methods.description: Resets the plugin updated flag, indicating synchronization.

methods.name: GetParamUlongValue_COSADataModel
methods.description: Retrieves ULong parameters for the COSA DataModel object (like Version, LoadStatus).

methods.name: int GetParamStringValue_COSADataModel(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext,char * ParamName,char * pValue,ULONG * pUlSize)
methods.description: Retrieves string parameters (ModuleName, Author, Description, SourceName) for the COSA DataModel object.

methods.name: SupportedDataModel_GetEntryCount
methods.description: Returns the count of entries for a supported data model table.

methods.name: SupportedDataModel_GetEntry
methods.description: Returns an entry handle for a given index in the supported data model table.

methods.name: SupportedDataModel_GetParamStringValue
methods.description: Retrieves string parameter values for the supported data model, such as URL, URN, or Features.

methods.name: BOOL CcspComp_GetParamUlongValue(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext,char * ParamName,ULONG * puLong)
methods.description: Gets ULONG component parameters like Version, State, Health from CCSP components.

methods.name: ULONG CcspComp_GetParamStringValue(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext,char * ParamName,char * pValue,ULONG * pUlSize)
methods.description: Gets string component parameters like Name, Author, DTXml.

methods.name: BOOL CcspComp_GetBulkParamValues(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext,char ** pParamArray,PSLAP_VARIABLE * ppVarArray,ULONG ulArraySize)
methods.description: Retrieves multiple component parameters in bulk as an array of SLAP_VARIABLEs.

methods.name: BOOL CcspComp_SetParamBoolValue(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext,char * ParamName,BOOL bValue)
methods.description: Sets boolean component parameters, e.g., Register capability.

methods.name: BOOL CcspLog_GetParamBoolValue(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext,char * ParamName,BOOL * pBool)
methods.description: Gets boolean logging parameters such as Enable.

methods.name: BOOL CcspLog_GetParamUlongValue(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext,char * ParamName,ULONG * puLong)
methods.description: Gets ULONG logging parameters such as LogLevel.

methods.name: BOOL CcspLog_SetParamBoolValue(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext,char * ParamName,BOOL bValue)
methods.description: Sets boolean logging parameters.

methods.name: BOOL CcspLog_SetParamUlongValue(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext,char * ParamName,ULONG uValue)
methods.description: Sets ULONG logging parameters.

methods.name: BOOL CcspLog_Validate(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext,char * pReturnParamName,ULONG * puLength)
methods.description: Validates logging configuration (stub always returns true).

methods.name: ULONG CcspLog_Commit(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext)
methods.description: Commits logging configuration changes by applying them.

methods.name: ULONG CcspLog_Rollback(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext)
methods.description: Rolls back logging changes (stub).

methods.name: BOOL CcspMem_GetParamUlongValue(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext,char * ParamName,ULONG * puLong)
methods.description: Gets memory usage parameters such as MinUsage, MaxUsage, and Consumed.

methods.name: BOOL CcspLog_GetBulkParamValues(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext,char ** pParamArray,PSLAP_VARIABLE * ppVarArray,ULONG ulArraySize)
methods.description: Retrieves bulk logging parameters such as Enable and LogLevel.

methods.name: BOOL CcspLog_SetBulkParamValues(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext,char ** pParamArray,PSLAP_VARIABLE * ppVarArray,ULONG ulArraySize,PULONG pulErrorIndex)
methods.description: Sets bulk logging parameters.
